{"tid":2500392,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"昨獲頒大獎今罪成 金堯如新聞大奬評審：查冊無罪 判決不損對報道嘉許","createTime":"2021-04-22T14:51:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T13:06:02.000Z","uid":240362,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"28dd32a697513d56af4ad87b1885139ff5d165dc","tid":2500392,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T14:51:57.000Z","msg":"蔡玉玲的案件宣判前夕，涉案報道《鏗鏘集－7.21誰主真相》剛奪得「金堯如新聞大奬」，有評審指判決不會影響獎項結果，但擔心記者未來再難以查冊採訪，如同「斬去」調查報道記者的手腳。各界亦開腔支持蔡玉玲，其中16名港台節目顧問團成員批評判決未有衡量公眾知情權及新聞自由重要性，歐盟駐港辦事處亦指法律不應用作扼殺正當新聞工作。<br />\n<br />\n今屆「金堯如新聞大奬」評審之一、金堯如新聞基金管理委員會秘書麥燕庭表示，今次兩個得獎新聞作品均以查冊做起點，其中鏗鏘集《7.21誰主真相》在電台電視組獲一眾評審給予各作品中最高分，代表各評審都肯定這個調查報道，方法和表達形式均專業和仔細，值得肯定和嘉許，今次法院裁決也不會影響今次獎項結果。<br />\n<br />\n她強調，至今仍不認為查冊有罪，又指法院判決只基於法例的狹窄定義，亦未考慮獲基本法保障的新聞自由，以至公眾利益。她相信，記者未來難以用查冊採訪，如同「斬去」調查報道記者的手腳。<br />\n<br />\n她更擔心，今次記者在運輸署查冊被判罪成後，其他政府部門會「有樣學樣」，日後公司、土地查冊亦會受限制，不但會損害香港的新聞自由，也會損害香港作為資訊自由中心地位。<br />\n<br />\n對於法官稱記者若要就車牌查冊去信運輸署署長，麥相信仍會受限於有關交通及運輸事宜的用途，但即使可去信提出申請，「咁即係話畀佢聽我做緊咩嘢故仔？甚至叫佢審埋個故仔？如果覺得故仔對政府冇咩害，就畀啲資料你；否則就『對唔住喇，根據條例，畀唔到你』。」<br />\n<br />\n另外，不同界別都在判決後先後開腔支持蔡玉玲，其中歐盟駐香港及澳門辦事處在Twitter發文指，蔡玉玲的定罪提醒社會，新聞自由並非理所當然，法律亦不應用來扼殺正當的新聞工作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210422/YM7T2JEBSFDE5ISYDCA6RG7SE4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210422%2FYM7T2JEBSFDE5ISYDCA6RG7SE4%2F&d=0rs6uxY5NhpkL%2Fcp6PdBrfRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=982a7508\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210422%2FYM7T2JEBSFDE5ISYDCA6RG7SE4%2F&h=cc46963f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210422/YM7T2JEBSFDE5ISYDCA6RG7SE4/</a>"},{"pid":"d40400f09f529d1f5287ee8b81a0e6579a1c5350","tid":2500392,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T14:57:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5f838d6b7235da8fd82c73ff899a0142573ef9c","tid":2500392,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T14:59:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32026a2ffc89b15d82915ae868ff5de37f9fde4c","tid":2500392,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T15:06:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"552d7c1b76cbb38359b0abb3a9115e7136b13b81","tid":2500392,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T15:38:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd14d52dad5441ae62a7d91de229a385f4adae24","tid":2500392,"uid":353489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T18:37:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"a0d39f044baff35120ea312fbb0266de660c41af","tid":2500392,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T18:38:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6242900ebb337a4c0b8e898249b0893fe4dac607","tid":2500392,"uid":363620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T18:55:17.000Z","msg":"查冊都唔俾查 唔通記者仲跑即時新聞咩 記者就係揭露被掩蓋嘅事實啦<br />\n<br />\n不過同當今政權講都係on9<br />\n佢就係想得翻啲吃喝玩樂版"},{"pid":"4e3d74626dac66e0d778dfe855ad860c